          <p>My very favorite presets get even better in Filmist 1.9. This update features a new version Portra 160 Pushed, plus updates to Agfaflex, Provia 400 and Velvia simulations. Gavin delves into the update in <a href="https://youtu.be/JmwtJhfa4Ww" target="_blank">his latest YouTube video</a>.</p>
          <p>Personally, I am finding the new F Velvia 100 to be exceptional on greenery, the perfect preset for summer forest rambles!</p>
