              <a href="https://support.google.com/domains/answer/13689670?hl=en">About the Squarespace purchase of Google Domains registrations</a>
            </dt>
            <dd>On June 15, 2023, Squarespace announced its intent to purchase domain registrations and related customer accounts from Google Domains. This sounds like complete bullshit to me. If you're using Google Domains as a registrar for your website, I strongly recommend migrating your registration to another registrar. We've been using <a href="https://www.namecheap.com/">NameCheap</a> for most of our domains; so far, they've been fine.</dd>

